        <title>General Description</title>
        
        <levelledPara>
          <title>Overview</title>
          <para>
            The Center Body is the primary structural component of the AMPEL360 AIR-T 
            Blended Wing Body (BWB) fuselage. It provides the main load-bearing structure 
            and houses critical systems including passenger cabin, cargo areas, and flight 
            control systems.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
        
        <levelledPara>
          <title>Key Features</title>
          <para>
            The Center Body integrates seamlessly with the wing structures to create the 
            distinctive BWB aerodynamic profile. It is constructed from advanced composite 
            materials with aluminum alloy reinforcements at critical load points.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
      </levelledPara>
